<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />Do not let me be humiliated, Yahweh; for I call out to you!</para>

<para style="q1">May the wicked be humiliated! May they be silent in Sheol.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="18" style="v" />May lying lips be silenced</para>

<para style="q1">that speak against the righteous defiantly</para>

<para style="q1">with arrogance and contempt.</para>
